---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: GolfSimMap" description="How we launched GolfSimMap and reached DR 13 in the first week.">
  <section class="pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-12">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-[#00f0ff] font-['JetBrains_Mono']">CASE STUDY</p>
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-4">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/golfsimmap-logo.png" alt="GolfSimMap logo" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl object-cover border border-[#2a2a3a]" loading="lazy" />
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-white font-['Space_Grotesk']">GolfSimMap</h1>
      </div>
      <p class="text-[#8b8b9a] text-lg mt-5 max-w-3xl">A directory website for indoor golf simulator venues in the US. Built for clean UX, SEO depth, and fast page speed.</p>

      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mt-10">
        <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5">
          <p class="text-[#5b5b6a] text-xs">Launch</p>
          <p class="text-white font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-2xl">Feb 2026</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5">
          <p class="text-[#5b5b6a] text-xs">Early authority</p>
          <p class="text-[#8b5cf6] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-2xl">DR 13</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-5">
          <p class="text-[#5b5b6a] text-xs">Core metric</p>
          <p class="text-[#00f0ff] font-['JetBrains_Mono'] text-2xl">Sub 1s pages</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="pb-20">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="bg-[#151520] border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-2xl overflow-hidden">
        <img src="/images/portfolio/golfsimmap-hero.png" alt="GolfSimMap homepage" class="w-full h-auto" loading="lazy" />
      </div>

      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-10">
        <div class="bg-[#151520]/50 border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-semibold mb-3 font-['Space_Grotesk']">What we built</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8b8b9a]">Directory architecture with state, city, and venue pages, structured metadata, and scalable content templates designed for search coverage.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#151520]/50 border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-6">
          <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-semibold mb-3 font-['Space_Grotesk']">Stack</h2>
          <p class="text-[#8b8b9a]">Next.js, Supabase, static category config, and performance-first implementation for fast load times and crawl efficiency.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10 bg-[#151520]/50 border border-[#2a2a3a] rounded-xl p-6">
        <h2 class="text-white text-xl font-semibold mb-3 font-['Space_Grotesk']">Result highlights</h2>
        <p class="text-[#8b8b9a]">After launch, the site reached DR 13 in about one week, with active indexing and backlink growth underway. The platform is now in growth mode focused on content expansion and authority building.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-10">
        <a href="https://golfsimmap.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-[#0a0a0f] bg-gradient-to-r from-[#8b5cf6] to-[#a78bfa] rounded-xl hover:shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(139,92,246,0.4)] transition-all">Visit Live Site</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
